title: John Henry and Savannah - Donald, Where's Your Trousers
description:
This is the song John Henry and Savannah sung together at the end of Terminator The Sarah Connor Chronicles S02E21.

I like it and I thought others might as well. I have included the WAV file for those that like to do their own encodes. If you don't want the WAV file don't download it.

I swear I spent more time setting up the torrent than I did working out how to pull the audio from the mkv file.
